TITLE: Approving Land Registry Split/Merge Requests with Digital Signatures
DESCRIPTION: Function that allows registrars to approve split/merge requests using cryptographic signatures. It verifies signature validity, checks if the signer has the appropriate role, and executes the request when enough approvals are collected.

