TITLE: Setting Up Vault Authentication and Policies
DESCRIPTION: This script configures AppRole authentication in HashiCorp Vault and creates a policy for the platform to access specific secret paths. It gives complete access to secrets in the ethereum, fabric, and ipfs paths.

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
# Enable AppRole auth method
vault auth enable approle

# Create platform policy
vault policy write btp - <<EOF
path "ethereum/*" {
  capabilities = ["create", "read", "update", "delete", "list"]
}
path "fabric/*" {
  capabilities = ["create", "read", "update", "delete", "list"]
}
path "ipfs/*" {
  capabilities = ["create", "read", "update", "delete", "list"]
}
EOF
```

